		<p><a href="https://www.elsevier.com/books/sports-travel-security/tarlow/978-0-12-805099-6" target="_blank"><img class="alignright" width="150" height="185" src="http://www.tourismandmore.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/sports-travel-security-book.jpg"/></a><strong><a href="https://www.elsevier.com/books/sports-travel-security/tarlow/978-0-12-805099-6" target="_blank">Sports Travel Security</a></strong><br>
by Peter Tarlow</p>
		<p>Sports Team Security examines the security needs for sports teams and events of all sizes. This groundbreaking book provides a fundamental model for sports team security that can be applied almost universally, from youth sports to the Super Bowl and World Cup.</p>

